Set of packaging related exceptions

See: Description

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    AnnotationMergingException  
    AnnotationsManifestMergingException
    Indicates an issue with AnnotationsManifests when merging Envelopes.
    DocumentMergingException  
    DocumentsManifestMergingException  
    EnvelopeClosingException
    Wrapper exception that encompasses any/all Exception encountered by Envelope during Envelope.close().
    EnvelopeMergingException  
    EnvelopeReadingException
    Wrapper exception that contains exceptions encountered during Envelope reading.
    InvalidEnvelopeException
    Indicates that there is an unrecoverable internal error with the Envelope.
    ManifestMergingException  
    MimeTypeMergingException  
    SignatureMergingException

    Indicates an issue with SingleAnnotationManifests when merging Envelopes.
